    <briefdescription>
<para>A set of key frames for a property that can be animated using <ref refid="classDali_1_1Animation_1ad0abd1b6c2d446b09d0921fbaf9551a8" kindref="member">Dali::Animation::AnimateBetween()</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This allows the generation of key frame objects from individual Property::Values. The type of the key frame is specified by the type of the first value to be added. Adding key frames with a different Property::Value type will result in a run time assert. @SINCE_1_0.0 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
